{"tid":1244103,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好問點解要衝 因為雨傘後你後悔左幾多年？","createTime":"2019-06-19T18:01:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T17:54:03.000Z","uid":3740,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d76406dde0c2ededd5a7a1ef4969f13e7030f6f1","tid":1244103,"uid":3740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:01:01.000Z","msg":"6月12日班黑警既嘴臉 依一世都唔會忘記 <br />\n打落示威者到從不手軟 催淚彈直接射落人群中間 槍口直接打頭 <br />\n唔好同我講佢地係到維持治安 佢地只係想打死班示威者 係惡魔<br />\n林鄭道歉 可以對住鏡頭笑 記者問題一樣都無答到 <br />\n李家超 盧一哥 唔關佢地事 可笑至極 <br />\n<br />\n5年過去左 雨傘當時期 我都以為係我地勝利 和理非係勝利關鍵 <br />\n原來係自己太天真 我唔想幾年後再後悔 <br />\n<br />\n6月21日 要寫上香港民主既新一頁"},{"pid":"dab15806c7308760c218e56fac0b288ae34bf425","tid":1244103,"uid":3740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:04:08.000Z","msg":"今次大家要明白 我地對抗既仲係腐敗既警權 依場杖唔係單單係對政府不滿咁簡單"},{"pid":"5b7dc980f97d590b2b0bd17423955a0a805d860c","tid":1244103,"uid":229425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:04:37.000Z","msg":"真，自從雨傘後個世界變咗黑白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4f0574c0f9b2e0b26af35acf60b9b787ef811d","tid":1244103,"uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:05:08.000Z","msg":"係時候一雪五年前金紫荊之恥"},{"pid":"e515e66f0707b7ec14ce883fe57ae627fc8de856","tid":1244103,"uid":3740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b7dc980f97d590b2b0bd17423955a0a805d860c","tid":1244103,"uid":229425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:04:37.000Z","msg":"真，自從雨傘後個世界變咗黑白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:06:37.000Z","msg":"曾經一刻 我真係以為贏左 <br />\n但原來100+200萬人都唔夠6月12日一日咁重要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7941583f86b12cf3d88ba3a2103474f0462cb5","tid":1244103,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/78MsPp